## CI/CD Configuration

### 1. GitHub Actions

```yaml
name: CI/CD
on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - uses: pnpm/action-setup@v2
        with:
          version: 8
      - run: pnpm install
      - run: pnpm test
      - run: pnpm lint
      - run: pnpm check:types
      - run: pnpm build
```

