- [ ] ESLint configured for all packages
- [ ] Testing configured and working
- [ ] Storybook configured
- [ ] Build scripts working
- [ ] Dependencies updated
- [ ] CI/CD configured
- [ ] Bundle analysis implemented
- [ ] Documentation updated
